        <h1 class="cd-h1" contenteditable="true">Explainable AI in federal capture: what audit-defensible looks like</h1>
        <p class="cd-dek" contenteditable="true">The federal AI procurement standard shifted this year. Six federal CIOs published explainability mandates. Most capture AI tools can't comply. Here's what audit-defensible actually means — and what to look for.</p>
        <div class="cd-grounding">
          <span class="cd-grounding-lbl"><i class="ti ti-link"></i>Grounded in</span>
          <span class="cd-chunk"><span class="cd-chunk-dot sig"></span>sg-12 · 6 CIO mandates</span>
          <span class="cd-chunk"><span class="cd-chunk-dot gtm"></span>GTM Hero</span>
