        <p class="cd-body-p" contenteditable="true">The federal AI procurement standard isn't going to soften. The CIOs that published these mandates are going to enforce them, and the inspectors general are going to test them in audits over the next 18 months. The capture teams that win in this environment will be the ones using AI that was architected for the standard — not retrofitted to it.</p>
